Invocation Name: voice four victory
des: WVFV (Voice for Victory) is a conservative Christian radio station operated under the ministry of Victory Baptist Church. We are based out of Roanoke Rapids, NC, in Halifax County. It is our desire to strengthen individuals and families in our community and around the world through this station. We play conservative Christian music and programming that you can trust 24/7!
